reviewText: These videos are avaialable for free viewing on the activity tv website, but i prefer to have a dvd we can watch in front of the big tv.  very helpful for the young (or old) aspiring juggler
I found this video to be exciting for me. I learned to juggle from a child's point of view and learning skills. Remember, "it is only easy if you know how". I now know how! Thank you ActivityTV.
